cookies.description:
Cookies are used to improve our website. If you grant permission, data collected for performance purposes will be processed by Vercel Analytics and Vercel SpeedInsight, and cookies such as language preference will be stored in your browser. The processed data by Vercel includes information about the country you are accessing from and the browser you are using, while your private IP address will not be collected. Clicking on the decline option will disable all cookies, and no cookies will be collected to improve our site or enhance your user experience.
&nbsp;
For more information, you can review our [Cookie Policy](/policies/cookie-policy) and [Privacy Policy](/policies/terms-of-privacy).
